_text = "It’s time to go. The camping trip is over. Say goodbye to all your friends. You don’t know it yet, but this will be your last camping trip with them before your friendships all fissel out.I’m going to move away 9 months from now.\n\nOur only connection soon transforms into text threads that grow further apart. Its as if our relationships only now exists inside a cell phone.\n\nAs we drive away from this campsite, I watch from afar as all my friends return to society. I watch our relationship grow apart, as if I’m still stuck behind at this campsite. Waiting for them in a place with no cell reception.\n\nMy memory of this place ends here."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MemoryTunnelRoom3, MemoryTunnelRoom4, false)
